WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:02.427
Well, good morning, family.

00:00:02.427 --> 00:00:05.040
I appreciate you joining me tonight.

00:00:05.040 --> 00:00:10.559
I could say good evening, or I could say good afternoon for some of you.

00:00:10.559 --> 00:00:12.720
I don't know; it's all over the world.

00:00:12.720 --> 00:00:14.537
That's why people go, 'You didn't say good morning.

00:00:14.537 --> 00:00:16.879
' So, I'm going to say good morning, family.

00:00:16.879 --> 00:00:20.340
Thank you for joining us again today.

00:00:20.800 --> 00:00:22.836
We'll talk about some stuff.

00:00:23.227 --> 00:00:25.667
I won't make it too long because it's already late.

00:00:25.667 --> 00:00:32.800
I've been really busy today, but I have a couple of things here for you.

00:00:32.800 --> 00:00:40.426
I'm really excited about what our Secret Service uncovered today.

00:00:41.466 --> 00:00:45.751
I believe that as a result of our prayer, I truly do.

00:00:45.751 --> 00:01:00.423
As the believing believer stands on the wall and prays for this nation, we see what I've told you in my spirit, what I felt that the Lord was showing us about something major.

00:01:01.520 --> 00:01:15.703
This looks like they stumbled upon something major as it was announced today by Homeland Security or by Secret Service or whatever.

00:01:15.703 --> 00:01:17.760
That was pretty amazing.

00:01:18.480 --> 00:01:27.990
The scheme, this plot, and this plan that they were trying to do to communicate secretly—I said through back hidden doors.

00:01:27.990 --> 00:01:31.653
Well, who knew it would be this kind of a back hidden door?

00:01:31.653 --> 00:01:33.129
I was like, 'Wow.

00:01:33.129 --> 00:01:40.320
' As it was being talked about in the media today, I told my wife, 'Isn't Jesus wonderful how this was uncovered?

00:01:40.320 --> 00:02:00.989
' I guess I don't want to say anything ever is an accident—by the hand of God, by the hand of God moving in our behalf to try to disrupt and cause great mass confusion and all kinds of plots and plans here.

00:02:06.840 --> 00:02:17.909
I believe in my spirit, when I'm praying over this even more today, that there's a lot more that will be uncovered in the days ahead, even with what they found.

00:02:17.909 --> 00:02:40.940
We will believe God tonight as a family that whatever else is out there, any other kind of hidden networking or other kind of apartment complex rooms or whatever, will be found by what they found today and in the past, whenever they found it.

00:02:40.940 --> 00:02:50.053
I was trying to make sense of that, if they found it today or if this was something that they just decided to announce today or whatever.

00:02:50.053 --> 00:03:15.369
But just the whole, all of it given nobody got hurt, and that there's going to be a whole bunch of trails to go out and find because they were even saying, as you will hear in just a minute, that there was a whole bunch of foreign governments that were involved in this and all kinds of stuff.

00:03:15.369 --> 00:03:16.629
So, it's pretty amazing.

00:03:16.629 --> 00:03:21.474
I don't know how many people heard about what happened in New York today.

00:03:21.474 --> 00:03:31.350
In the comment section, tell us, did you hear about what happened in New York today?

00:03:45.110 --> 00:03:45.500
What are they saying?

00:03:45.500 --> 00:03:47.840
Oh, no, I don't know.

00:03:47.840 --> 00:03:53.835
Nobody has a clue, huh?

00:03:53.835 --> 00:03:57.760
Well, how many people are here right now?

00:03:57.760 --> 00:03:58.520
2,700.

00:03:58.520 --> 00:04:08.560
Okay, go ahead and play the clip of what was uncovered today in New York City and tell us if you can hear it.

00:04:08.560 --> 00:04:10.510
'Sir, how are you?

00:04:10.510 --> 00:04:11.680
' 'Good.

00:04:11.680 --> 00:04:14.169
How are you?

00:04:14.169 --> 00:04:20.356
' 'What they uncovered was a major network of telecommunications devices that can be used anonymously and encrypted.

00:04:20.356 --> 00:04:24.479
They can be used to shut down cell towers.

00:04:24.479 --> 00:04:27.919
They could be used to not allow access to EMS and 911.

00:04:30.089 --> 00:04:34.310
You see, what we found when we went in there were shelves of these SIM cards and SIM servers that were used to run this network.

00:04:41.400 --> 00:04:41.653
It can't be understated what this system is capable of doing.

00:04:41.653 --> 00:04:50.663
Like I said, it can take down cell towers so then no longer can people communicate, right?

00:04:50.663 --> 00:05:00.720
You can't use Waze, you can't use text message, you can't use your cell phone.

00:05:04.373 --> 00:05:13.291
And if you coupled that with some sort of other event, right, associated with an attack or, you know, use your imagination there, it could be catastrophic to the city.

00:05:13.291 --> 00:05:23.829
Definitely nation-state, foreign governments communicating over that network to known criminals in the United States and known organized crime, known cartels, and terrorist groups were using this network to run their communications anonymously and encrypted.

00:05:23.829 --> 00:05:29.360
Let me just explain that this is no longer a threat.

00:05:29.360 --> 00:05:31.029
We've taken this network down.

00:05:31.029 --> 00:05:32.800
Could there be others?

00:05:32.800 --> 00:05:33.600
Right.

00:05:41.970 --> 00:05:45.700
It would be unwise to think that there are not other networks out there being made in other cities in the United States.

00:05:45.700 --> 00:05:49.580
And that's going to be part of our investigation.

00:05:49.580 --> 00:05:53.120
We're going to run down every single lead.

00:05:53.120 --> 00:06:02.800
We want to identify, locate, and take down these criminals that are setting up these networks.

00:06:02.800 --> 00:06:09.120
My message to them is: if you're involved in this, we're coming for you.

00:06:09.120 --> 00:06:15.220
' Did you see all of those SIM cards and how it was all linked together?

00:06:16.000 --> 00:06:19.954
And even in the news article, they said this was funded very well.

00:06:19.954 --> 00:06:21.600
It was funded.

00:06:24.389 --> 00:06:28.160
I can't even imagine what that cost, but a major, major, major something here was uncovered today.

00:06:43.360 --> 00:06:44.160
This was not just a normal, small-minded person doing this; this is somebody who is pretty smart to hook all that up.

00:06:44.160 --> 00:06:56.550
They knew what they were doing and for it to be encrypted so that they could hide and communicate with this and that nobody could hear what they were saying.

00:06:56.550 --> 00:07:04.759
Remember, I told you, every time I'm praying in the spirit, I hear back rooms.

00:07:04.759 --> 00:07:12.639
They're able to bypass so that they're not able to be seen or heard.

00:07:12.639 --> 00:07:25.306
Well, as we hear in part, see in part, and as we're praying into this, look, just like the man said—I don't know who that man was, but that is very thought out.

00:07:25.306 --> 00:07:45.246
And I don't know how long that's been going on, but what he was saying was, and even in the article that Diana was reading to me, that they had the capability to text everyone in the United States of America within 12 minutes.

00:07:45.246 --> 00:08:29.476
Everyone in the United States of America could receive a text message within 12 minutes from this machine, whatever that was, that they could push the button and it would send a text message or have so much texting going on from that area that it would actually affect the whole infrastructure of the city of New York, so that if there was a major event that took place, some kind of activity, it would make it impossible for people to reach the 911 operators to ask for help.

00:08:29.476 --> 00:08:38.799
They could jam up the police station and all this stuff with that machine that you saw there.

00:08:38.799 --> 00:08:47.467
All glory to God, folks, that that was uncovered and that was brought to justice today, and that God is—I'm telling you, prayer changes things.

00:08:52.549 --> 00:08:57.543
As we intervene by praying in the spirit, I told you we are called to pray and that the power of prayer will change things.

00:09:09.131 --> 00:09:10.320
And I see this as an answer to prayer today, that we see what I told you, praying over those five major cities.

00:09:10.320 --> 00:09:13.560
One of them was New York, as I told you.

00:09:32.890 --> 00:09:37.147
And the Lord said, 'As you pray, you will change things and the course of things.

00:09:37.147 --> 00:09:45.799
' And I believe God is raising us up for such a time as this.

00:09:53.279 --> 00:09:55.662
And that's why he said, 'If you try to shut the watchmen's mouths up as we call to prayer—a call to prayer, a call to repentance, a call to seek Jesus—they're only hurting themselves.

00:09:55.662 --> 00:09:58.537
' So, we see a result of prayer today.

00:10:00.350 --> 00:10:01.400
I just believe that.

00:10:12.068 --> 00:10:19.020
And there's much more to follow.

00:10:19.020 --> 00:10:28.532
I believe as they go through those SIM cards, in the article they said they have to go through all 100,000 SIM cards.

00:10:28.532 --> 00:10:31.977
I'm like, that's 100,000 cell phones.

00:10:46.551 --> 00:10:46.800
I mean, each SIM card represents a cell phone.

00:10:46.800 --> 00:11:04.337
So, if they go through, they said they'll have to go through each one and they'll be able to see the text messages and all the things that were said secretly through each phone number that was all intertwined into a major scheme.

00:11:04.337 --> 00:11:06.439
So, isn't that amazing what God did today?

00:11:09.559 --> 00:11:09.760
I just want you all to know the Lord is on the throne.

00:11:09.760 --> 00:11:16.079
He is up there, and I'm telling you, it may be—I was just like, 'Thank you, Father.

00:11:16.079 --> 00:11:18.480
' I know in my spirit there's more.

00:11:19.577 --> 00:11:22.857
I know in my spirit that there'll be more in the days ahead that will be uncovered.

00:11:22.857 --> 00:11:30.640
This is just the beginning of the first domino of what we're doing in prayer, that we're able to uncover and expose the plan of the wicked.

00:11:30.640 --> 00:11:32.400
Isn't that awesome?

00:11:40.274 --> 00:11:40.616
So much more to follow in the name of Jesus.

00:11:46.731 --> 00:11:46.959
There is no rock that's big enough for them to hide under; all hidden things will be revealed by prayer.

00:11:49.720 --> 00:12:06.329
And as we pray and fast and seek the Lord, He said, 'If my people, who are called by my name, will humble themselves and pray and turn from their wicked ways, then we will hear from heaven, and He will heal our land.

00:12:06.329 --> 00:12:15.148
' And I believe this is—like I said, I keep saying it over and over again—number two of what happened.

00:12:15.148 --> 00:12:22.091
Today, we see President Trump going to the UN.

00:12:25.943 --> 00:12:31.610
And you know, they tried to dishonor him by even turning the escalator off, so he would not be honored with that escalator going up.

00:12:31.610 --> 00:12:38.569
They turned it off right when he stood there getting ready to get on.

00:12:43.611 --> 00:12:44.103
I said, 'That's not a coincidence.

00:12:44.103 --> 00:12:51.039
Somebody was being rude, making our First Lady walk up those stairs like that.

00:12:51.039 --> 00:12:55.839
' I said, 'Whoever did that should be fired immediately.

00:12:55.839 --> 00:13:03.360
' I know that was on purpose.

00:13:12.480 --> 00:13:12.746
You know that was on purpose, because that kind of stuff doesn't just happen by accident.

00:13:28.943 --> 00:13:29.279
The President of the United States just walks up to it and they just turn the escalator off?

00:13:41.670 --> 00:13:42.040
I said, 'Come on now.

00:13:42.409 --> 00:13:43.739
It's just immature crap.

00:13:43.739 --> 00:13:46.240
' We see that happen to him, and, whatever.

00:13:46.240 --> 00:13:59.920
And then they turned off his teleprompter so he had to speak from the heart, which I think is funny to see him speak like that when he's up there telling all those other nations they are going to hell.

00:13:59.920 --> 00:14:04.149
I thought some of the things he says are really funny.

00:14:04.149 --> 00:14:06.040
Do you have that clip?

00:14:10.480 --> 00:14:10.739
You guys can't laugh because I'll start coughing.

00:14:10.739 --> 00:14:12.880
Do you have that son?

00:14:12.880 --> 00:14:16.983
We were laughing about it because he was so bold today.

00:14:30.789 --> 00:14:31.063
You know, he was unscripted because he didn't read off that teleprompter.

00:14:31.063 --> 00:14:32.160
Is it there?

00:14:32.160 --> 00:14:35.246
Who saw him say that?

00:14:35.246 --> 00:14:39.279
Did anybody else hear him say that?

00:14:39.279 --> 00:14:43.486
Well, the bottom line is he stood with Israel.

00:14:43.486 --> 00:14:51.519
And that's what we were praying and believing God for, that our nation will stay a sheep nation in the name of Jesus.

00:14:59.893 --> 00:15:00.240
And so we believe that as we bless Israel, the blessing of the Lord comes upon our land.

00:15:00.240 --> 00:15:02.480
I didn't say an administration.

00:15:02.480 --> 00:15:10.010
I said, 'As the nation of America stands with Israel, I believe there's a blessing behind it.

00:15:10.010 --> 00:15:12.980
' Listen, it's funny what he says here.

00:15:12.980 --> 00:15:13.640
Do you have it?

00:15:13.640 --> 00:15:14.299
Yeah.

00:15:14.299 --> 00:15:17.599
'Filled with so-called asylum seekers who repay kindness.

00:15:25.348 --> 00:15:25.531
And that's what they did.

00:15:25.531 --> 00:15:26.529
They repaid kindness with crime.

00:15:26.529 --> 00:15:31.908
It's time to end the failed experiment of open borders.

00:15:31.908 --> 00:15:34.840
You have to end it now.

00:15:45.458 --> 00:15:45.849
See, I can tell you, I'm really good at this stuff.

00:15:45.849 --> 00:15:49.569
Your countries are going to hell.

00:15:49.569 --> 00:15:54.799
In America, we've taken bold action to swiftly shut down uncontrolled migration.

00:15:54.799 --> 00:16:03.736
Once we started detaining and deporting everyone who crossed the border and removing illegal aliens from the United States, they simply stopped coming.

00:16:03.736 --> 00:16:05.724
They're not coming anymore.

00:16:05.724 --> 00:16:10.952
We're getting a lot of credit, but they're not coming anymore.

00:16:10.952 --> 00:16:14.133
' He's just funny.

00:16:22.340 --> 00:16:22.790
I think it's funny.

00:16:22.790 --> 00:16:28.699
You know, when you don't have a teleprompter, you start just talking.

00:16:28.699 --> 00:16:30.205
He's just funny.

00:16:33.209 --> 00:16:33.698
I mean, I don't know.

00:16:33.698 --> 00:16:41.982
Some of you might not think that's funny, but I think it's funny.

00:16:41.982 --> 00:16:44.629
But we saw him stand behind Israel today.

00:16:44.629 --> 00:16:55.280
We saw him stand by what I knew in my spirit that he would do, warning the other people and them saying, 'We need to have peace in Gaza.

00:16:55.280 --> 00:16:58.880
We need to have peace in these areas.

00:16:58.880 --> 00:17:08.870
' But he's like, 'We need to release the hostages that they've been holding for over—going on, I don't know, is this three years?

00:17:08.870 --> 00:17:10.430
Two, three years.

00:17:10.430 --> 00:17:12.170
' It's ridiculous.

00:17:12.170 --> 00:17:24.720
These men and women who are still being held—I think he said twelve of them—they should be with their families in the process of peace.

00:17:26.045 --> 00:17:31.866
And then they asked, 'Should NATO countries shoot down Russian planes or whatever if they cross over into areas they shouldn't?

00:17:31.866 --> 00:17:32.986
' And he said, 'Yes.

00:17:32.986 --> 00:17:36.347
' So, you know, there's a lot of escalation there.

00:17:36.347 --> 00:17:44.440
What I told you I feel will turn into World War III in the days ahead.

00:17:48.080 --> 00:17:48.480
I pray that it does not.

00:18:01.019 --> 00:18:01.319
I pray for peace over the whole world.

00:18:01.319 --> 00:18:12.800
But we know what the Bible says, that there will be escalations of wars and rumors of wars.

00:18:12.800 --> 00:18:16.126
There will be plagues, pestilences, and all these things.

00:18:16.126 --> 00:18:25.337
But this is the beginning of sorrows, and the Lord told us this was coming.

00:18:25.337 --> 00:18:29.143
So, we're seeing it unfold.

00:18:29.143 --> 00:18:40.780
But as we prayed last night, does anybody remember what was said in last night's prayer time that was glorious?

00:18:40.780 --> 00:18:49.232
I'll go right into that real quick, and we'll talk about some other things and pray for a little bit.

00:18:49.232 --> 00:18:53.451
Last night, I saw the cloud, and the cloud started to build.

00:19:06.390 --> 00:19:06.640
It was the size of a car at the time when I first saw it on the edge of heaven.

00:19:23.897 --> 00:19:24.125
I could see it start to grow, and the cloud began to grow with such intensity and so quickly that it started to fill up the whole area of the vision.

00:19:24.125 --> 00:19:30.799
It looked like a raincloud, but it got larger and larger and larger.

00:19:36.046 --> 00:19:36.480
I could see it, and it was taking shape.

00:19:36.480 --> 00:19:46.972
All of a sudden, drops of rain started to fall, and you could see the rain falling in the rays of the light coming from behind the cloud.

00:19:56.057 --> 00:19:56.446
I could see the rain begin to fall, just starting to sprinkle.

00:19:56.446 --> 00:20:05.505
But I heard the sound of an abundance of rain upon the nations of this earth.

00:20:13.711 --> 00:20:21.440
And all of a sudden, I could hear the rain in the spirit realm, and you could smell it.

00:20:21.440 --> 00:20:25.679
You could feel the rain falling upon me.

00:20:26.106 --> 00:20:29.253
I could feel it as it was raining.

00:20:37.467 --> 00:20:37.893
And He said, 'I looked at Africa, and I could see the African people.

00:20:37.893 --> 00:20:51.146
They were in tribal outfits, and they had their hands raised, worshiping the Lord.

00:20:51.146 --> 00:20:56.227
' And some of them were twirling.

00:21:13.747 --> 00:21:14.373
And as they were doing that, I saw the rain pouring down on them in Africa as they were worshiping.

00:21:14.373 --> 00:21:22.960
I could see the water running down their faces and all down their arms and their bodies.

00:21:31.920 --> 00:21:32.400
And I could see the rain of the Holy Spirit raining down on them.

00:21:51.450 --> 00:21:51.805
It was coming.

00:21:51.805 --> 00:22:00.987
It was in their mouth; it was on their lips.

00:22:10.200 --> 00:22:10.480
And I could see the rain, and they were saturated with the presence and the glory of the Lord.

00:22:18.286 --> 00:22:18.571
And their skin began to shine as the glory was on their faces and the rain was there.

00:22:28.080 --> 00:22:31.211
And I heard the Spirit of the Lord say, 'This is the former and the latter rain together, and another wave of the glory is coming upon the nations of the earth.

00:22:31.211 --> 00:22:44.016
' I saw then the rain begin to spread throughout everywhere: Asia, South America, America, and it was glorious.

00:23:02.000 --> 00:23:02.320
And I could hear the rain.

00:23:07.589 --> 00:23:08.057
And that's whenever I kept hearing Him say, 'Can these bones live?

00:23:08.057 --> 00:23:13.622
Can the dry bones of the spiritually dead live?

00:23:13.622 --> 00:23:19.179
Can the dry bones of the spiritually dead live?

00:23:25.613 --> 00:23:26.026
The seeker-friendlies, the lukewarm, can these bones live?

00:23:26.026 --> 00:23:46.204
' The Lord was saying again, as I could hear the sound of a mighty waterfall, just like when you hear rain in the distance and it's just pouring—you just hear it, I could hear it—and He said, 'The rain's coming.

00:23:46.204 --> 00:23:48.240
It's no longer coming, son; it's here.

00:23:48.240 --> 00:23:53.400
It's no longer coming, son; it's here.

00:23:53.400 --> 00:23:56.933
' That's what the Lord said.

00:23:56.933 --> 00:23:59.280
'You'll start to see the first drops.

00:23:59.280 --> 00:24:09.919
' Even when it was with Charlie's funeral, his homegoing service, He said, 'You're seeing the first drops fall.

00:24:09.919 --> 00:24:15.770
You're seeing the first drops fall of a great outpouring of My Spirit upon all flesh.

00:24:15.770 --> 00:24:23.611
You're going to see what you never thought you—I mean, what you've always dreamed you would see.

00:24:23.611 --> 00:24:29.730
' But as I was looking, the Lord allowed me to see pressure.

00:24:29.730 --> 00:24:32.000
Persecution comes for His name's sake.

00:24:42.640 --> 00:24:42.944
I saw Canada.

00:24:42.944 --> 00:24:47.982
I saw the freedom to be able to say what you want to say.

00:24:47.982 --> 00:24:59.760
Even in our country, the First Amendment, the right to freedom of speech being challenged in the days ahead on social media platforms.

00:24:59.760 --> 00:25:07.299
But mainly in this vision, I saw it being challenged in Australia and in Canada.

00:25:10.960 --> 00:25:11.280
And I saw an olive press.

00:25:12.560 --> 00:25:20.200
And as the olive press was pressing the olives, I saw it being tightened and tightened and tightened.

00:25:30.080 --> 00:25:30.360
And as the olive press was pressing down upon the olives, it was springing forth beautiful olive oil.

00:25:35.080 --> 00:25:44.192
And this was a representation, I believe, of a new outpouring and a new pressure on the church.

00:25:44.192 --> 00:25:49.494
Out of the pressure of persecution came beautiful, fresh olive oil.

00:26:03.954 --> 00:26:04.376
I saw great darkness.

00:26:04.799 --> 00:26:43.049
I saw great trial for some, testing your faith, being persecuted for your faith in a way that this generation, a lot of Western society, would not be familiar with, compared to what maybe the Far East has experienced: a great persecution from China, from the Iron Curtain that's on North Korea, the darkness that tries to suppress Christianity all around the world, from Iranian Christians that are tortured and murdered without any kind of sympathy at all.

00:26:59.360 --> 00:27:16.480
And I saw that a lot of people think if they're persecuted in a comment section—which I have been in the past, and I don't even read them anymore—but through persecution, through these keyboard warriors, the Lord said that's not true persecution compared to when you're dragged down the street by a motorcycle driving down the street at 35 or 40 miles an hour and you're being dragged to death.

00:27:16.480 --> 00:27:19.393
That's great persecution, do you understand?

00:27:19.393 --> 00:27:23.080
Or losing your head for what you believe.

00:27:23.080 --> 00:27:24.640
That's persecution.

00:27:24.640 --> 00:27:27.160
That's martyrdom.

00:27:30.480 --> 00:27:36.799
And that's what the Lord was showing me: the Western culture doesn't understand that kind of persecution.

00:27:36.799 --> 00:27:55.275
But as your freedom of speech and other areas are tested in the days ahead, I saw great pressure coming from Canada upon the citizens in the days ahead.

00:28:09.919 --> 00:28:10.209
And I saw an olive pressing, and I saw the church going through a metamorphosis of growth spiritually.

00:28:10.209 --> 00:28:30.850
But as you take for granted the very freedoms that you have on a day-to-day basis, when that freedom is challenged and you're called to stand for something and make a choice, versus being a coward and hiding behind something—either you stand for something or you lose it.

00:28:30.850 --> 00:28:36.292
Either you get a backbone like a crowbar or you lose it.

00:28:52.600 --> 00:28:53.013
